'''Greg Winters''' provided the cover art for the [[LucasArts]] game ''[[Star Wars: Rebel Assault]]''. The image, depicting [[Rookie One]]'s participation in the [[Battle of Kolaador]], was later used on [[The Topps Company, Inc.|Topps's]] ''Star Wars Galaxy Series 3'' trading cards.

He also provided illustrations for the book-and-record ''[[The Further Adventures: Planet of the Hoojibs]]''.

